ğŸ§© Troubleshooting Checklist
Use Packet Tracerâ€™s ipconfig to verify device IPs.

Ping between endpoints for connectivity/isolation.

Simulate cable/switch failuresâ€”observe mesh and ring recovery.

Review VLAN/ACL settings for extended security (if configured).

